{"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC11","role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Bonjour Network Discovery and Connectivity"},"abstract":[{"text":"Bonjour, also known as zero-configuration networking, enables automatic discovery of computers, devices, and services on IP networks. A wide range of Apple’s products-from iMacs and MacBooks to AirPort Base Stations and Time Capsules, Apple TVs to iPhones, iPod touches and iPads-use Bonjour for streamlined and reliable networking. Learn how to use Bonjour to make it easy for your applications to publish, discover, and resolve network services.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/211\/","type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-211-bonjour-network-discovery-and-connectivity"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-211-Bonjour-Network-Discovery-and-Connectivity","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","image